rows.name:
This is Theoscaldia, Teos Aure's
royal palace.

rows.label: tlk44310182_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You. Outlanders. Luxuria is a
tranquil place. You will not be
permitted to disturb the peace.

rows.label: tlk44310182_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If you don't follow our rules, you'll be
deported with the utmost expedience.
Bear that in mind.
